ygData.messageBody:
Thanks so much for the invite! You are the only response I got from that post
actually. If I were a PVP person, I'd take you up on that. However, I am just
one of the those wimpy girls who'd rather just battle it with the monsters
rather than people too. My partner is even worse. She's bad enough now when
she gets killed! <grin>

I will keep your email though, because who knows? I could end up getting bored
on the regular servers and need a little more excitement in my life... heheh.

How long have you two been playing? What types of chars do you have? I've
actually got six chars spread between two servers: Brell and Erollisi. A
pally, ranger, druid, shaman, warrior and enchanter. Almost all mid- to
high-teens.

If I come over to Rallos, what name should I look for? Take care of yourself
and talk to ya soon.

Chris
